    <h2>Branding</h2>
    <p>The BreakLine program is very rigorous, intense, and effective. The symmetry and boldness of the mark helps show that as well as providing a sense of balance and stability that one can expect from a BreakLine program. The triangles that make up the mark point forward and encourage people to continue on a path to reach their dream career and never look back. The lowercase wordmark gives the logo a softer and friendlier tone, inviting potential students to apply. This logo is also very universal which will allow them to expand into other fields and target people with non-military backgrounds as well.</p>
